  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAccording to this PR: https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1837\r\n\r\nWe should bound the error response, however we still have it as a string type which is unbounded. \r\n\r\nSee here: https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/master/beacon_node/eth2_libp2p/src/rpc/codec/ssz.rs#L59\r\nand here: https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/master/beacon_node/eth2_libp2p/src/rpc/codec/ssz.rs#L318\r\n\r\n\r\n",
